Note: I know &quot;Adam Curtis Ultimate Collection&quot; sounds very egotistical. But I didn't know what to call this torrent. It isn't &quot;complete&quot; since it doesn't include the files one can get from archive.org. It isn't &quot;best&quot; since it aims for compatibility too. So I picked &quot;ultimate&quot; because that doesn't actually mean anything specific.


